Package main.java.vlashchevskyi.exam.resolver

Supplies classes to remove time overlaps within booking requests group.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OverlapResolver
    OverlapResolver is interface contains the method to remove booking request from collection if its time is crossed with others.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicOverlapResolver
    BasicOverlapResolver class removes requests from Map if they are crossed with others by booking time.
    ConcurrentOverlapResolver
    ConcurrentOverlapResolver class uses PoolExecutor to remove requests with time overlaps from Map.
    OverlapsRemoveTask
    OverlapsRemoveTask class creates a task to remove wrapped booking request and is designed for multithreading.
    Resolver
    Resolver class provides the method to remove booking records from List.
    ResolverFactory
